Epimerites I free. Epigynum 35–40 long, 86–90 wide. Head of spermatheca with 5–6 rounded denticles, without collar; proximal part of primary spermaduct monotonously enlarged to head of spermatheca, distal part straight; secondary spermaducts 10–12 long (
Fig. 15H
). Posterior margins of epimerites IIIa with long narrow extension. Epimerites IVa present, long. Anal opening with adanal sclerites.
